@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<section class="inner-banner bg_img"
         style="background: url('/images/66868cfc051ae1720093948.jpg') center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="inner-banner-content">
            <h2 class="title">About</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section padding-top padding-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-4 mb-md-5 gy-4">
            <div class="col-lg-7 col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-content">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <h2 class="title">Know Few Words About SRC Travel Agencies</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>SRC Travel Agencies is a leading private transportation company that operates nationwide. With several branches across different locations, SRC provides efficient transportation services, catering to customer requirements through a variety of bus options, including Express, Luxury, and Volvo (A/C and Non A/C).</p>

                    <div class="section-header"
                         style="margin-bottom:20px;color:rgb(119,119,119);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;">
                         <br /><br />
                        <h3 style="font-size:18px;color:rgb(66,66,72);">Current System Challenges</h3>
                        <p>
                            Currently, SRC processes ticket bookings manually at bus counters or onboard the buses. This approach makes it difficult to track bookings across the country and manage seat availability in real-time. Additionally, maintaining customer details and the variety of bus services offered is challenging without an integrated online system.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <p style="color:rgb(119,119,119);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:16px;">
                        SRC aims to enhance their operations by developing an online ticket booking system. This system will allow customers to book tickets either at local booking counters or online, enabling real-time updates of bookings and seat availability. The system will store information such as bus details, customer data, and bookings in a centralized database, accessible from all branches.
                    </p>
                    <p style="color:rgb(119,119,119);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:16px;">
                        The application will also calculate ticket prices based on factors like bus type, distance traveled, and customer age, while incorporating automatic discounts for specific age groups. An admin panel will be responsible for managing bus details, employee records, and ticket pricing, ensuring streamlined management and an improved customer experience.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-5 col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-thumb">
                    <img src="~/images/668687dc5c7ad1720092636.jpg" alt="Know Few Words About SRC Travel Agencies">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-details">
            <div class="item">
                <h4 class="title">Why Choose SRC Travel Agencies</h4>
                <p>SRC Travel Agencies offers a wide range of benefits to its customers, ensuring a comfortable and reliable travel experience.</p>

                <ul class="info" style="margin-top:15px;margin-left:15px;">
                    <li style="list-style:disc;padding:3px 0px;">Free Cancellation</li>
                    <li style="list-style:disc;padding:3px 0px;">Instant Refunds</li>
                    <li style="list-style:disc;padding:3px 0px;">Easy & Quick Bus Booking</li>
                    <li style="list-style:disc;padding:3px 0px;">Exciting Cashback & Bus Offers</li>
                    <li style="list-style:disc;padding:3px 0px;">Best Price Assured</li>
                    <li style="list-style:disc;padding:3px 0px;">24/7 Customer Assistance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="faq-section padding-top padding-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-8">
                <div class="section-header text-center">
                    <h2 class="title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions, we have the answers! Check below for our most frequently asked questions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="faq-wrapper">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-title">
                            <span class="icon"></span>
                            <h5 class="title">How do I make a reservation for a bus?</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-content">
                            <p>To make a reservation, simply visit our booking page, select your desired bus and route, and follow the prompts to complete your booking.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-title">
                            <span class="icon"></span>
                            <h5 class="title">What payment methods do you accept?</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-content">
                            <p>We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards, PayPal, and bank transfers to ensure a smooth transaction.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-title">
                            <span class="icon"></span>
                            <h5 class="title">Can I cancel or modify my booking?</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-content">
                            <p>Yes, you can cancel or modify your booking up to 24 hours before the departure time. Please refer to our cancellation policy for more details.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="faq-wrapper">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-title">
                            <span class="icon"></span>
                            <h5 class="title">What happens if my bus is late?</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-content">
                            <p>In the event of a delay, our customer service team will keep you updated via email or SMS. We strive to ensure that all our buses run on time.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-title">
                            <span class="icon"></span>
                            <h5 class="title">Are there any age restrictions for traveling?</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-content">
                            <p>There are no age restrictions for traveling with us, but children under the age of 12 must be accompanied by an adult.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

